9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE ARKANSAS UNDERGROUND FACILITIES
10 DAMAGE PREVENTION ACT; TO REVISE MEMBERSHIP IN THE
11 ONE CALL CENTER UNDER THE ARKANSAS UNDERGROUND
12 FACILITIES DAMAGE PREVENTION ACT; AND FOR OTHER
13 PURPOSES.
